        "purpose": "english_translation",
        "value": "Of which: 516.286 koku deducted as an overall write-off, being the shortfall from waste land and river-erosion damage (荒地川欠不足高). A subtraction internal to the combined kokudaka; the 荒地川欠不足高 gloss appears lower in the same column."
